4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring specialists with no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week, accommodating up to 18 students per class. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with advanced topics such as cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The course also covers risk management using data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an officially recognized certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. Stop.